<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="panel panel-info">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4>Here you can add new articles to Storage.io. All files will be trusted timestamped. Please make sure that
                you provide metadata as much as possible! You can also upload supplementary data of all kinds (e.g. datasets)
            under Add -> Additional Data. The data also may be not article related.</h4>
        </div>
